    <item>
      <title>哈里斯誓言建立美国关键矿产储备并推出激励措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-vows-to-create-us-critical-minerals-stockpile-incentives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯誓言要建立国家关键矿产储备，她表示，从电池到国防系统等各个领域所使用的材料对于经济和国家安全都是必需的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-vows-to-create-us-critical-minerals-stockpile-incentives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:17:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登会见越南最高领导人，暗中反华</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-meets-vietnam-s-top-leader-in-veiled-counter-china-play</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国努力对抗中国在亚洲的经济和安全影响力之际，总统乔·拜登会见了越南共产党总书记苏林，庆祝与越南“关系进入新时代”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-meets-vietnam-s-top-leader-in-veiled-counter-china-play</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国参议院罕见投票判定 Steward 首席执行官藐视法庭罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-senate-holds-steward-ceo-in-criminal-contempt-in-rare-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议院周三投票决定，判定 Steward Health Care 首席执行官藐视法庭罪，因其未能就其在该破产医院运营商财务崩溃中所扮演的角色作证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/us-senate-holds-steward-ceo-in-criminal-contempt-in-rare-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 21:59:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登与泽连斯基在美国会面，公布 3.75 亿美元武器计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-announces-new-ukraine-weapons-package-with-zelenksy-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国周三宣布向乌克兰提供价值 3.75 亿美元的新武器装备，包括火箭系统和火炮弹药、装甲车和反坦克武器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/biden-announces-new-ukraine-weapons-package-with-zelenksy-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 21:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默将会见美国商界领袖，呼吁英国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/starmer-to-meet-us-business-chiefs-as-he-touts-for-uk-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将于周四会见美国企业高管，包括黑石公司总裁乔恩·格雷 (Jon Gray)、摩根大通资产管理公司首席执行官玛丽·卡拉汉·埃尔多斯 (Mary Callahan Erdoes) 和美国银行首席执行官布莱恩·莫伊尼汉 (Brian Moynihan)，这位英国首相希望吸引投资来提振英国疲软的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/starmer-to-meet-us-business-chiefs-as-he-touts-for-uk-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国会通过临时拨款法案避免政府关门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/speaker-johnson-turns-to-democrats-to-avert-government-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在议员们从华盛顿赶赴 11 月大选之前进行最后的竞选活动之前，国会议员们周三避免了一场对政治造成损害的政府关门，并迅速通过了一项短期联邦拨款法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/speaker-johnson-turns-to-democrats-to-avert-government-shutdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 20:35:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在经济演讲中将自己塑造为亲劳工“资本家”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-casts-herself-as-pro-labor-capitalist-in-economic-pitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯誓言要成为企业高管和员工的盟友，这位民主党总统候选人概述了她对“机会经济”的愿景，即资助新行业投资并建设中产阶级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/harris-casts-herself-as-pro-labor-capitalist-in-economic-pitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 20:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔火灾威胁富裕地区，迫使总统回家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基多的富裕社区仍然面临火灾威胁，在消防员与厄瓜多尔首都的森林大火搏斗之际，学校已转为在线教学，直至本周末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ecuador-fires-threaten-rich-neighborhoods-force-president-home</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 19:31:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国罕见在太平洋进行洲际弹道导弹试验以展示实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-launches-icbm-with-dummy-warhead-into-pacific-ocean</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国向太平洋发射了一枚洲际弹道导弹，这似乎是中国四十年来首次公开进行此类试验，此举可能会引起美国方面的不安，因为美国正试图在联合国大会上影响世界领导人的态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/china-launches-icbm-with-dummy-warhead-into-pacific-ocean</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 03:53:41 GMT</pubDate>
